name: Room Lender
overview: Room Lender is an excellent, user-friendly resource for finding and listing vacation rentals, condos, beach houses, villas or furnished apartments anywhere in the world. RoomLender.com is a continuously evolving online platform that does not settle to satisfy only today’s accommodation standards. Originating in Chicago, but rapidly expanding in Miami, San Francisco and pretty much everywhere independent and business travelers need a short term house. RoomLender.com offers services for guests who want more than just a hotel room. Since its creation only a few years back, RoomLender.com has moved forward in sync with the technology, trying to foresee new demands, while constantly adjusting with the feedback from users. We not only offer a trustworthy environment both for travelers and hosts, where everyone can have an enjoyable experience, but also strive to become the meeting place of choice for travelers and hosts worldwide.
